          <lg n="1"><l rend="center" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-1" n="1">I.<lb/><hi rend="display-initial">A</hi> Widow kept a Favourite Cat,</l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-2" n="2">At first a Gentle Creature,</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-3" n="3">But when he was both sleek and fat,</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-4" n="4">With many a Mouse and many a Rat,</l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-5" n="5">He soon disclos'd his Nature.</l><l rend="center" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-6" n="6">II.<lb/>The <hi rend="italics">Fox</hi> and he were Friends of Old,</l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-7" n="7">Nor could they now be pated;</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-8" n="8">They Nightly slunk to rob the Fold,</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-9" n="9">Devour'd the Lambs, the Fleeces sold,</l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-10" n="10">And <hi rend="italics">Puss</hi> grew Lion hearted.</l><l rend="center" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-11" n="11">III.<lb/>He scratcht her Maid, he stole the Cream</l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-12" n="12">He tore her best lac'd Pinner;</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-13" n="13">Nor <hi rend="italics">Chantieleer</hi> upon the Beam,</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-14" n="14">Nor <hi rend="italics">Chick</hi>, nor <hi rend="italics">Duckling</hi> 'scapes when</l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-15" n="15">Invites the <hi rend="italics">Fox</hi> to Dinner.</l><l rend="center" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-16" n="16">IV.<lb/>The <hi rend="italics">Dame</hi> full wisely did decree</l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-17" n="17">For fear he should dispatch more,</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-18" n="18">That the false Wretch shou'd worry'd be</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-19" n="19">But in a sawcy manner he</l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-20" n="20">Thus answer'd like a <hi rend="italics">L────ch──re</hi>.</l><l rend="center" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-21" n="21">V.<lb/><hi rend="italics">Must I, against that Right and Law,</hi></l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-22" n="22"><hi rend="italics">Like </hi>Pole-Cat<hi rend="italics">, vile be treated;</hi></l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-23" n="23">I, who so long with Tooth and Claw,</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-24" n="24">Have kept Domestick Fools in Awe.</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-25" n="25">Have kept Domestick Fools in Awe.And Foreign Foes defeated</l>.<l rend="center" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-26" n="26">VI.<lb/><hi rend="italics">Your Golden Pippins, and your Pies,</hi></l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-27" n="27">How oft have I defended;</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-28" n="28">'Tis true, the Pinner which your prize,</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-29" n="29">I tore in Frolick, to your Eyes</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-30" n="30">I tore in Frolick, to your EyesI Never Harm Intended</l>.<l rend="center" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-31" n="31">VII.<lb/><hi rend="italics">I am a Cat of Honour</hi>────Stay,</l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-32" n="32">Quo' she no longer parly;</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-33" n="33">Whate're you did in Battle slay,</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-34" n="34">By Law of Arms became your Prey</l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-35" n="35">I hope you won it fairly.</l><l rend="center" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-36" n="36">VIII<lb/>Of this we'll grant you stand acquit,</l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-37" n="37">But not of your Outrages;</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-38" n="38">Tell me, Perfidious was it fit</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-39" n="39">To make my Cream a Perquisite</l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-40" n="40">And steal to mend your Wages?</l><l rend="center" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-41" n="41">IX.<lb/>So flagrant is they Insolence,</l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-42" n="42">So vile they Breach of Trust is,</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-43" n="43">That longer with thee to dispense,</l><l xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-44" n="44">Were want of Power or want of Sence.</l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-153-F18--line-45" n="45">Here <hi rend="italics">Towzer</hi>!──── do him Justice,</l></lg>
        </div>
